The '''white-fronted swift''' ('''''Cypseloides storeri''''') is a species of [[Swift (bird)|swift]] in the family [[Apodidae]]. It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Mexico]]. Its natural [[habitat]] is subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]]s.

